{"tid":537271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞外賣仔大罷工！","createTime":"2018-01-22T14:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T11:18:20.000Z","uid":29314,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"58532f69dd09bef0011dbd3897e6d8000160465a","tid":537271,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:14:20.000Z","msg":"網上外賣服務商Deliveroo下午有工人發起罷工。約50名Deliveroo外賣工人，疑不滿更改工作時間及薪酬安排，令他們收入大減，下午聚集在公司位於上環蘇坑街的辦公室地下。罷工工人大部份為南亞裔人士"},{"pid":"e8b3c2fd7efab21cfb8cf77e90f51a9272d7d42a","tid":537271,"uid":11447,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"支持佢地翻鄉下！"},{"pid":"40cb7e285da8f2b972f57648c2c0ed2890e1f356","tid":537271,"uid":41508,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"721c1388e839c88fd48bcf66cf96a85c76612efa","tid":537271,"uid":53498,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"蝻都團結過港豬"},{"pid":"c730629e2db0feddeabbcf46a6aebe9a8b7a5b01","tid":537271,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:19:00.000Z","msg":"送返去南亞餵狗"},{"pid":"556eaa88362a26b6076abadfc5a6b759c1706551","tid":537271,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2332cfb01c8fb9f904474cfb4e25d7c762f950a","tid":537271,"uid":55458,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:44:39.000Z","msg":"黃種賤畜會幫老細ot"},{"pid":"8ea41e8b529c24bf9bd353036f44d4827aefaf80","tid":537271,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:47:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"378b4790bbd0a884a9f56d2d338fff8c1d2c4d1d","tid":537271,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"721c1388e839c88fd48bcf66cf96a85c76612efa","tid":537271,"uid":53498,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"蝻都團結過港豬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e933e93d968178958043e6d1622a4dfdf23d1d","tid":537271,"uid":123711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:49:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f0b08e41c1f79d6476d294778d360ef4a964c73","tid":537271,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:52:13.000Z","msg":"有員工解釋，他們屬自僱人士，每小時酬勞約75元，以工作12小時為例，以往不論所接外賣訂單多少都有約900元($75X12)收入。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可是改用新的電子平台後，疑因公司滅少了非繁忙時段可容許的當值人數上限，令不少員工每天實際可領取酬勞的時數大減（例如工人原本返朝七晚七，但轉用新電子平台後每日中段可能有3至數小時毋須當值，致酬勞減少），從而令月人大大減少。"},{"pid":"0708899747b8b49362aae231b0c86a310fdc0c2e","tid":537271,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180122/large/1516609637_1970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180122%2Flarge%2F1516609637_1970.jpg&h=4b45b29f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9961311ab61d0b767c90418d5feeef555756233","tid":537271,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:55:34.000Z","msg":"南vs財團<br />\n連登憤青今次企邊面？"},{"pid":"a95dc2fd893fb10609a3deb0504d1fc298103132","tid":537271,"uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/075500_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F075500_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3a224336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他表示車手們都是自僱人士，早已沒有任何福利，而且維修費、油錢統統由車手承擔。他指公司從前亦會資助抄牌的罰款、每月有$200油錢的補貼、每月一次的飯聚，但這些福利於近日統統取消，而這次實行編更制限制他們工時，更是在剝削他們。"},{"pid":"e8b16b4d085934bf54a1847b4ed75a61bf0c8e02","tid":537271,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南vs財團<br />\n連登憤青今次企邊面？</blockquote><br />\n點解做deliveroo同ubereat都係阿差居多？"},{"pid":"ae5c68d5a8f66147908cb3f526cf68d91e6591b3","tid":537271,"uid":1059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T01:20:45.000Z","msg":"南亞狗執港女屍射D基因入去就識"},{"pid":"0323e6798a48a5e6ef46fb8b8f4783e7ddd70d58","tid":537271,"uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T01:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/092602_a4fdbfe38c54c757b01a83a60de3c6b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F092602_a4fdbfe38c54c757b01a83a60de3c6b3.jpg&h=1a5ffdda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ed5c3c28b0c7504bf4224ffe98af8aec36db6f4","tid":537271,"uid":144843,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T01:27:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1021fca2e3ab27096e36d726ccbb1ad1801d929","tid":537271,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T01:30:29.000Z","msg":"編左更其實好大機會自動變員工"},{"pid":"1ab9d60abb341f902a66cf25b179364b1b69c562","tid":537271,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8b16b4d085934bf54a1847b4ed75a61bf0c8e02","tid":537271,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南vs財團<br />\n連登憤青今次企邊面？</blockquote><br />\n點解做deliveroo同ubereat都係阿差居多？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"你問點解 <br />\n<br />\n香港兩個碌既合格率唔高 <br />\npizza hut 17000-23500月薪 <br />\n<br />\n佢地個牌係印度巴基轉過香港 安全意識有幾高 明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f0157b78ca4e4fa519e8363d5db86fe1691314","tid":537271,"uid":46328,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a1021